20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-101.42, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 6-101.42. A. For the 2025-2026 school year, each
23 school district shall provide to every support employee, as defined
24 in paragraph 8 of Section 1-116 of this title, with a salary of less
